53_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"海兒高貴登場。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96ce47285134ac1913defcc8450c8934/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_9_53_51_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"海兒因做《中年好聲音4》的評審而人氣急升。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e27930f8642047c4303232b9e2ad8af0/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_9_53_50_PM_2_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"海兒仙氣造型登場。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e1f3614ab6b5d169c58559656f18756c/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_9_53_50_PM_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"久未在香港舞台演出的陳偉霆(William)與VIVA四位師妹合作跳唱。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e004b7b566f90566f9a13d1f5025b2ba/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_30_39_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"陳偉霆久違在香港演出。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3775d337638b1d06eb3448cb85631ace/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_30_42_PM_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"陳偉霆與VIVA合作。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26c79137b2129976adcc615bad2119a6/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_30_42_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"VIVA是英皇新晉女團。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cf39c9b8fb9cb7a3ece888eb4a089058/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_30_45_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"陳偉霆與VIVA跳唱《女皇》、《Do You Wanna Dance》。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9422b6973c599fc6de70bf8140e71457/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_30_46_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"陳偉霆17歲加入英皇。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9aefa65259b6af46ee0134f9501b8318/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_30_47_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"英皇一姐容祖兒壓軸登場。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4c98a8c90e17a6646ec1d55039f54cb7/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_35_50_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"容祖兒獻唱金曲勁有壓台感。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/64850d6b5f4cc2f970e21ef5498a9ddc/2026-05/WhatsApp_Image_2026-05-03_at_10_35_51_PM.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"容祖兒將一連兩晚現身《25+英皇群星演唱會》。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/n